(13, 1, '2017-11-07 11:32:51', '2017-11-07 11:32:51', '\n	<p>961<br />\nwebsites built<br />\nand counting<br />\n<button><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/portfolio.png\" alt=\"portfolio\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" /> View Portfolio</button></p>\n	<p>We Build WordPress Websites That Sell!</p>\n<p>We make sure that your website design ideas will turn into reality through the help of our highly<br />\nexperienced in-house WordPress developers. Every wordpress website we create goes through quality<br />\nassurance process to give you a great design and functionality for the user interface of your site or blog.</p>\n<p><button>Free consultation today</button></p>\n	<p>Have Experienced<br />\nDesigners and Developers<br />\nCreate Your Own WordPress Website<br />\nSome of our WordPress services include, but not limited to the following</p>\n				<img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ipad.png\" alt=\"ipad\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"721\" width=\"827\"  />\n	<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Theme</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">WordPress Theme<br />\nCustomization</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/service-1.png\" alt=\"WordPress Theme Customization\" width=\"169\" height=\"134\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Transform your below-average wordpress theme into a power-packed and highly flexible theme with the help of our expert WordPress developers. Whatever adjustments you want to happen, we\'ll do our very best to turn your vision into reality.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><button>Get A Quote</button></p>\n	<p style=\"text-align: right;\">PSD to Theme</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">WordPress Website<br />\nDevelopment</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/service-2.png\" alt=\"WordPress Website Development\" width=\"169\" height=\"134\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our WordPress website development team members are skilled when it comes to technical work that makes your website run the way it\'s supposed to. Whether you have an existing website that you would like to change or would like to create an entirely new website, our expert WordPress development team can handle that.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><button>Get A Quote</button></p>\n	<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Plugin</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">WordPress Plugin<br />\nDevelopment</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/service-3.png\" alt=\"WordPress Plugin Development\" width=\"169\" height=\"134\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Use the latest and the greatest plugins on your WordPress site without slowing down your speed or cluttering your page\'s interface. We will help you choose the WordPress plugins that\'s best run on your website, that will bring you the leads, and help engage your customers at every visit.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><button>Get A Quote</button></p>\n	<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Premium</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Support and<br />\nMaintenance</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/service-4.png\" alt=\"Support and Maintenance\" width=\"169\" height=\"134\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our team will not leave you in the dark. If you ever run into a problem once your site is up and running or have a question about your website, we will always be here to assist you. We can also provide updates such as content adding/editing, plugin and theme upgrades.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><button>Get A Quote</button></p>\n				<img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/folio.png\" alt=\"folio\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"771\" width=\"845\"  />\n	<h3>Start your business\' online journey right with an easy-to-manage WordPress website</h3>\n<p>Start your business\' online journey right with an easy-to-manage WordPress website created by our in-house Filipino WordPress developers and designers. We offer both white label/reseller and direct services for all types of businesses.</p>\n<p>We\'re here to provide online and business solutions whenever and wherever they\'re needed.</p>\n	<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/bar.png\" alt=\"bar\" width=\"150\" height=\"100\" /></p>\n<h3>Our White Label Services</h3>\n<p>Our white label services are targeted towards offshore or foreign website development and design companies looking for online staff in other areas! If you\'re loaded with work but down on staff, we can take the workload off your shoulders.</p>\n<p>Here are a few reasons why you\'d like to start a white label partnership with us at WordPress Designer</p>\n	<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"55\" height=\"57\" />It\'s more affordable<br />\nthan having to hire in-house staff</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"55\" height=\"57\" />It\'s less time<br />\nconsuming as well</p>\n<hr />\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/3.png\" alt=\"3\" width=\"55\" height=\"57\" /></p>\n<p>We do the work for you<br />\nso you can better manage your time and resources</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/4.png\" alt=\"4\" width=\"55\" height=\"57\" />We save you the effort and time<br />\nyou\'d spend putting up hiring ads and waiting for qualified applicants</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/5.png\" alt=\"5\" width=\"55\" height=\"57\" />We can assign a dedicated team or staff<br />\nto work solely for you and your projects</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/6.png\" alt=\"6\" width=\"55\" height=\"57\" />We offer customise WordPress<br />\nwebsite packages for personalized and unique websites</p>\n<hr />\n				<img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Import.png\" alt=\"Import\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"865\" width=\"831\"  />\n	<h3>Our Direct Services</h3>\n<p>If you own a business and want to start establishing your online presence, we can get our team to help you out and build your own WordPress website. We build websites for a variety of businesses and industries, both local and global.</p>\n<p>Just tell us what you need, and our staff of WordPress developers and WordPress designers in the Philippines will get right to it. Here are some of the packages we offer here at WordPress Designer.</p>\n	<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">A team of not less than 30 Web Professionals with WordPress experience ranging from 2-9 years.</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/wd/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/team.png\" /></p>\n', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2017-11-16 06:40:28', '2017-11-16 06:40:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wd/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
